collectionMetadata.name: Gazetted Hotel Statistics - Summary, Monthly
collectionMetadata.description:
This report shows key gazetted hotel statistics, including room nights, Standard Avg. Occupancy Rate, Standard Avg. Room Rates and Revenue Per Available Room, for the specific month and year selected.
2015 Figures for the hotel industry are preliminary estimates.
Source: STB’s survey on ‘Return of Hotel on Room Lettings and Food & Beverage Sales Turnover’ as at 27 Jun 2016.
